The paper discusses challenges related to cybersecurity and data quality in synchrophasor devices, which are used for real-time monitoring and operational visibility of smart grids. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
